4 "105.711. 1. There is hereby created a "State Legal Expense Fund" which shall consist
5 of moneys appropriated to the fund by the general assembly and moneys otherwise credited to
6 such fund pursuant to section 105.716.
7 2. Moneys in the state legal expense fund shall be available for the payment of any claim
8 or any amount required by any final judgment rendered by a court of competent jurisdiction
9 against:
10 (1) The state of Missouri, or any agency of the state, pursuant to section 536.050 or
11 536.087 or section 537.600;
12 (2) Any officer or employee of the state of Missouri or any agency of the state,
