14 commissions, and members of the Missouri National Guard upon conduct of such officer or
15 employee arising out of and performed in connection with his or her official duties on behalf of
16 the state, or any agency of the state, provided that moneys in this fund shall not be available for
17 payment of claims made under chapter 287;
